《'''幸运儿'''》（{{lang-en|Lucky Guy}}）是一部由[[諾拉·艾芙倫|諾拉·艾芙倫]]编剧的戏剧，于2013年，也就是她去世的那一年首映。这是艾芙倫的最后一部作品，也是[[汤姆·汉克斯|汤姆·汉克斯]]首次登上[[百老汇|百老汇]]舞台，这为他赢得了{{tsl|en|Tony Award for Best Actor in a Play|托尼奖最佳戏剧男演员}}的提名。<ref>{{cite news|last=Hetrick|first=Adam|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/nora-ephrons-lucky-guy-starring-tom-hanks-may-head-to-london|title=Nora Ephron's Lucky Guy, Starring Tom Hanks, May Head to London|work={{tsl|en|Playbill||}}|date=2013-05-17|accessdate=2014-08-31|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140913010817/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/nora-ephrons-lucky-guy-starring-tom-hanks-may-head-to-london|archivedate=2014-09-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2013/04/01/175923676/tom-hanks-and-nora-ephrons-lucky-guy-make-their-broadway-debuts|title=Nora Ephron's 'Lucky Guy' And Tom Hanks Make Their Broadway Debuts|accessdate=2013-09-17|date=2013-04-01|publisher=[[全国公共广播电台|全国公共广播电台]]|author=Lunden, Jeff|archive-date=2013-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130604091139/http://www.npr.org/2013/04/01/175923676/tom-hanks-and-nora-ephrons-lucky-guy-make-their-broadway-debuts|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name=LGIBDB>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibdb.com/production.php?id=493577|title=Lucky Guy|accessdate=2013-04-27|date=|publisher=[[互聯網百老匯資料庫|互聯網百老匯資料庫]]|archive-date=2013-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509061533/http://www.ibdb.com/production.php?id=493577|dead-url=no}}</ref>

